===Etymology===
From {{der|en|frm|théorie}}, from {{der|en|LL.|theōria}}, from {{der|en|grc|θεωρία|t=contemplation, speculation, a looking at, things looked at}}, from {{m|grc|θεωρέω|t=I look at, view, consider, examine}}, from {{m|grc|θεωρός|t=spectator}}, from {{m|grc|θέα|t=view}} + {{m|grc|ὁράω|t=I see, look}} [i. e. θέαν ὁράω (théan horáō, “see, look at a view; survey + genitive”)].

